Date:   Sat Jan 30 10:08:50 2021 +0100

    Forbid invalid Activity requirements.
    
    The unit activities "Unused Road", "Unused Railroad", "Unused",
    "Unused Airbase" and "Unused Patrol" aren't valid values for the "Activity"
    requirement type.
    
    See hrm Bug #918765

