Date:   Fri Oct 23 00:09:35 2020 +0300

    Add '.serv' extension to file created by /write
    
    Only files with '.serv' extension can be read by /read command, so
    it should always be on files created by /write.
    
    Requested by S.C. L.
    
    See hrm Bug #677584
    
