commit 9e181103e4ce83b6f3947360863513c8c11c3b4d
Author: Marko Lindqvist <cazfi74@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu Jan 9 07:28:31 2020 +0200

    Fix sign-compare compiler warning from genlist_sort()
    
    See hrm Bug #855389
    
