Date:   Mon Dec 16 06:32:48 2019 +0200

    Add C11 threads configure check
    
    C11 threads are the preferred threading model.
    
    See hrm Feature #852681
    
    Signed-off-by: Marko Lindqvist <cazfi74@gmail.com>

