commit c25079945c7c20b9b2148a6d8713bee23000591b
Author: Marko Lindqvist <cazfi74@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Oct 15 05:49:15 2018 +0300

    gtk3x: Get rid of obsolete gtk_event_box_new() calls
    
