commit 93ded081ee5e60406dcecba31ba740e18de2348b
Author: Marko Lindqvist <cazfi74@gmail.com>
Date:   Sat Mar 3 01:30:25 2018 +0200

    sdl2: set width of empty string to 0 in utf8_str_size()
    
    See hrm Bug #684183
    
