commit 65df080f59609cd37e098d86d39692c0c795a0f0
Author: Marko Lindqvist <cazfi74@gmail.com>
Date:   Tue Sep 5 02:47:15 2017 +0300

    Fix tutorial description to speak of civ2civ3 ruleset
    
