commit 326d51a65bbaa6050421d56d7cc99a2990fb5e8d
Author: Sveinung Kvilhaugsvik <sveinung84@users.sourceforge.net>
Date:   Mon Jun 26 16:46:41 2017 +0200

    Non enemy city blocks "Bombard" and "Attack".
    
