r35425 | sveinung | 2017-05-06 21:59:02 +0100 (Sat, 06 May 2017) | 13 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/data/civ2civ3/README.civ2civ3
   M /trunk/data/civ2civ3/effects.ruleset
